\id 2TH - Mbula
\h 2 Amǝ Tasalonika
\toc3 2Tas
\toc2 2 Amǝ Tasalonika
\toc1 2 Amǝ Tasalonika
\mt2 Ɓaria Cauterǝa mala Bulǝs aban ká a ban
\mt1 AMƏ TASALONIKA
\imt1 Mǝncau
\im Zuriki mala ɗenyicau amur cau mala nyare yiu mala Kǝrǝsti ka, lidǝmba nǝ kúnɓuàna aɓa ikǝlisiya mǝnana a Tasalonika ka. \bk Ɓaria Cautera mala Bulǝs aban ká aban Amǝ Tasalonika \bk* ka, bang cau amur twale mala aɓwana mǝnana ama, pwari yiu mala Mǝtalabangŋo ka angŋa dǝmba yina. Bulǝs gilǝki mǝnia yì cau à ne anggo ka, aban lǝmdǝia aɓwana ama, kaniama Kǝrǝsti nǝ̀ nyare nǝ̀ yiu ka, túró mǝɓane andǝ ɓealɓikea ka à nǝ̀ ká a dǝmba à nǝ̀ ngga ɓiki pa aɓata nggwamnati mala ɓeɓwa mǝnana nda aɓa sǝmbǝrǝa, à tunǝki ama <<Ɓwa mala Cauɓikea>>, mǝnana nǝ̀ ɓínǝì Kǝrǝsti ka.
\ip Yì, mǝ'mishan ngga, tsǝkcau nǝ rǝcandǝa ama ndanǝ ɓoaro aɓwana mǝnana à kǝ ɓal mǝnia yì cau ka, ɓǝa tamsǝ kusǝia aɓa paɓamuru malea, ko ɓǝa kutia do ká-mǝɓane andǝ nutanni ka, ɓǝa kǝ pak túró nǝ buia ace linǝ ɓamuria kǝla mǝnana Bulǝs andǝ aɓi amǝtúró pak ka, sǝ ɓǝa lidǝmba nǝ do pěmǝɓoarne.
\iot Agir mǝnana a ɓālǝi ka
\io1 Mǝncau\ior 1:1-2\ior*
\io1 Ɓwangsǝban andǝ lǝmdǝ earnǝban\ior 1:3-12\ior*
\io1 Akwarkiru amur yiu mala Kǝrǝsti\ior 2:1-17\ior*
\io1 Cau ɓakɓabum amur do nǝ ɓealu mala Kǝrǝsta\ior 3:1-15\ior*
\io1 Masǝlǝatacau\ior 3:16-18\ior*
\c 1
\s1 Makkun mala Bulǝs
\p 
\v 1 Mǝnia yì cauterǝa ka, pur nǝban Bulǝs andǝ Silas andǝ Timoti.
\p Aban ká aban ikǝlisiya mala amǝ Tasalonika, aɓwana mala Ɓakuli Tár sǝm andǝ Mǝtalabangŋo Yesu Kǝrǝsti.\f + \fr 1:1 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Atúró 17:1\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 2 Ɓǝ̀ ɓwamuru andǝ dorǝpwala mala Ɓakuli Tár sǝm andǝ Mǝtalabangŋo Yesu Kǝrǝsti, do atà wun.
\s1 Ɓakɓabum aɓa tanni
\p 
\v 3 Wun amǝ'eam sǝm, dumǝna sǝm púp ɓǝ̀ sǝm nggǝ ɓwangsǝ Ɓakuli a koya pwari, ace wun, sǝ anggo ka ndanǝ ɓoaro acemǝnana paɓamuru ma'wun ngga, nda rǝ lidǝmba kǝ̀rkǝ́r, sǝ earcearǝu mǝnana wu ndanǝi arǝarǝ wun ngga ndarǝ gulo.
\v 4 Ace mani ka, sǝm nǝ́ ɓamur rǝ sǝm ngga, sǝm nggǝ jali nǝ wun aban a'ikǝlisiya mala Ɓakuli. Sǝm nggǝ jali ace came ma'wun kàngkàng andǝ paɓamuru ma'wun aɓalǝ apatanni mǝnana wu kǝ kúmô, andǝ adomǝkwane mǝnana wu kǝ dumnǝ gandǝrǝu aɓalǝia ka.
\p 
\v 5 Amǝnia ka à lǝmdǝ ama Ɓakuli kǝ pak ɓashi male nǝ mǝsǝcau, sǝ a masǝlǝate ka nǝ̀ tsǝk wun wu nǝ̀ duk aɓwana mǝnana à kàrǝ́na à nǝ̀ kutia Domurǝm male mǝnana wu kǝ nu tanni ace ka.
\v 6 Ɓakuli ka, mǝ'mǝsǝcau na: Nǝ̀ yia mbwe ka aɓwana mǝnana à kǝ pa wun tanni ka, nǝ tanni,
\v 7 sǝ wun mǝnana wu kǝ nu tanni ka nǝ̀ yia pa wun usǝlǝo sǝ nǝ̀ pa sǝm gbal. Nǝ̀ yia pak mǝnia ka a pwari mǝnana Mǝtalabangŋo Yesu nǝ̀ yia pusǝna rǝì nǝi nǝ kuli aɓa bǝsa mǝ earke, nǝ amǝturonjar mǝcandǝe male atè.
\v 8 Nǝ̀ yia ɓasha aɓwana mǝnana kat à súrǝ̀ Ɓakuli raka, andǝ amana à ɓinǝ kpata Cau Amsǝban mala Mǝtala sǝm Yesu ka.
\v 9 Yia ka, à nǝ̀ pea wia tanni mala kiɗikiban mǝnana málá male pà kàm raka. À gauwuni tārǝia andǝ Mǝtalabangŋo andǝ tá mala rǝcandǝa male\f + \fr 1:9 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Isha 2:10\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 10 a pwari mǝno nǝ̀ yiu nǝi ace ak gulo andǝ ɓwangsǝkiban a bu aɓwana male mǝnana tària andǝ amǝnana kat à pà ɓamuria a baní ka. Wun gbal ka wu nǝ̀ pa aɓalǝia, acemǝnana wu earnǝ cau mǝnana sǝm bangga wun amurí ka.
\p 
\v 11 Nda gir mǝnana tsǝa koya pwari ka, sǝm nggǝ pakka wun hiwi. Sǝm nggǝ zǝmbi Ɓakuli ɓǝ̀ tsǝk wun, ɓǝ̀ wu dukdo mǝnana karǝ arǝ ulang do mǝnana tunǝ wun ace ka, sǝ ɓǝ̀ pa wun rǝcandǝa mala lùmsǝ pakki agir mǝɓoarne mǝnana kat paɓamuru ma'wun tsǝk wun a pě ka.
\v 12 Anggo ka, lullǝ Mǝtala sǝm Yesu nǝ̀ kum gulo nǝban wun, sǝ wu nǝ̀ kum gbal nǝbaní, nǝ ɓwamuru mala Ɓakuli ma'sǝm andǝ Mǝtalabangŋo Yesu Kǝrǝsti.
\c 2
\s1 Ɓwa mala Cauɓikea
\p 
\v 1 Sǝm nggǝ earce lǝmdǝa wun gir amur cau mala nyare yiu mala Mǝtala sǝm Yesu Kǝrǝsti, andǝ dapi ma'sǝm a banɓwáná a baní.\f + \fr 2:1 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 1Tas 4:15-17\xt*\ft .\f* Sǝm nggǝ zǝmba wun, wun amǝ'eamrǝarǝu ama,
\v 2 wu kǝa kaurǝa arǝ dǝurǝo ɗang. Sǝ ɓǝ̀ ɓabum wun ɓǝ̀ kǝa lo, nǝ cau mǝnana aɓea ɓwana na ama Pwari mala Mǝtalabangŋo angŋa dǝmba yina pale ka ɗàng. À nǝ̀ gandǝ bang ama à sǝni aɓa bangŋo, ko à oe a kún ɓeɓwa, ko à ɓalli aɓa ɓè cauterǝa mǝnana à twali ama pur nǝban sǝm ngga.
\v 3 Wu kǝa eare ɓǝ̀ kǝɓwa swarki wun ɗàng ko bǝti. Acemǝnana mǝno yì pwari ka pà nǝ̀ yiu peatu ɗang she ɓǝ̀ masǝlǝata Mgbicau arǝ Ɓakuli yina, sǝ Ɓwa mala Cauɓikea pusǝna rǝì, mǝno yì ɓwa mǝnana dupî ká kìɗìkì ka.
\v 4 Yì ka, nda ɓiu-mǝbura mǝnana kǝ loasǝ ɓamúrì amur Ɓakuli andǝ agir mǝnana kat aɓwana kǝ peri abania ka. Yàle nǝ̀ kutio a Ndàmǝgule mala Ɓakuli nǝ̀ duk kam, nǝ̀ na ama yì nda Ɓakuli.\f + \fr 2:4 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Dan 11:36\xt*\ft .\f*
\p 
\v 5 Ɓalǝ wun kasǝ mbo ama ǝn bangga wun cau amur amǝnia yi agir ka mǝnana mǝ nda atà wun ɗiɗyal ka?
\v 6 Sǝ wu sùrǝ́nà rǝ gir mǝnana kǝ tamsǝi mǝnia yì Ɓwa mala Cauɓikea arǝ pusǝrǝi ado ka. À eari wi ɓǝ̀ pusǝrǝi ado ɗàng sheɓǝ̀ pwari mǝnana à tsǝki wi yi pangŋǝ̀nà ka.
\v 7 Rǝcandǝa mala ɓealɓikea ka, angŋa dǝmba nǝ̀ nggǝ pak túró aɓa sǝmbǝrǝa, sǝ anggo ka, nǝ̀ ueo aɓa sǝmbǝrǝa she ɓǝà gǝshina ɓwa mǝnana akiyì njar male ka.
\v 8 Sǝ à nǝ̀ yia lǝmdǝí, yì Ɓwa mala Cauɓikea, mǝnana Mǝtalabangŋo Yesu nǝ̀ wal-luí nǝ yálí kúni, sǝ nǝ̀ kiɗiki rǝcandǝa male nǝ̀ nyesǝi ɓà, nǝ́ tǎ mala ɓoarɓwa mala yiu male ka.\f + \fr 2:8 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Isha 11:4\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 9 Yì Ɓwa mala Cauɓikea man ngga, nǝ̀ yiu nǝ rǝcandǝa mala Shetan, nǝ̀ yia pakki agir-ndǝlǝki, andǝ agir-lǝmdǝa, andǝ agir-gyambǝliban mǝ'nyirnì ɗàngɗáng.\f + \fr 2:9 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Mat 24:24\xt*\ft .\f*
\v 10 Yì ka, nǝ̀ pak túró nǝ koya nggaman swarkiban mǝnana ɓealɓikea kǝ yiu nǝi ka, amur aɓwana mǝnana à kǝ ká nǝ ká kìɗìkì ka. Amǝnia yì aɓwana ka, à nǝ̀ kìɗìkì, acemǝnana à ginǝ ak mǝsǝcau sǝ à ginǝ earce mǝsǝcau a ɓabumia, mǝnana nda nǝ̀ yinǝia ɓǝà kum amsǝban ngga.
\v 11 Ace mani ka, Ɓakuli nǝ̀ tasǝia wia swarkiban mǝcandǝe, à nǝ̀ earnǝ nyir.
\v 12 Anggo ka aɓwana mǝnana kat à ginǝ earnǝ mǝsǝcau, à pak banɓoarnado aɓa ɓealɓikea ka, à nǝ̀ kasǝia wia ɓashi lú.
\s1 Wu tamsǝ kusǝ wun kàngkàng // wun amǝkpata Yesu
\p 
\v 13 Sǝ sǝm ngga, ndanǝ ɓoaro ɓǝ̀ sǝm nggǝ pakki Ɓakuli yàwá ace wun, wun amǝ'eamrǝarǝu mǝnana Mǝtalabangŋo earkiyi acea raka. Ɓakuli ka tàrki wun kǝla aɓǝla agir mǝdǝmbe ace amsǝ wun, ɓǝ̀ wu duk aɓwana male, nǝ rǝcandǝa mala Bangŋo male, sǝ nǝ paɓamuru ma'wun arǝ mǝsǝcau ka.
\v 14 Yì nǝ̀ tunǝ wun, nǝ Cau Amsǝban mǝnana sǝm hamnǝi a ban wun ngga, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ wu kum kāmbe aɓa gulo mala Mǝtala sǝm Yesu Kǝrǝsti.
\v 15 Ace mani ka, wun amǝ'eamrǝarǝu, wu tamsǝ kusǝ wun kàngkàng, wu bwal mǝsǝcau mǝnana sǝm kania wun kat aɓa bang cau, andǝ cauterǝa ka.
\p 
\v 16 Sǝm nggǝ zǝmba ama Mǝtala sǝm Yesu Kǝrǝsti nǝ nggearǝì, andǝ Ɓakuli Tár sǝm mǝnana earce sǝm, sǝ aɓa ɓwamuru male ka, pana sǝm girikiban mǝnana málá male pà kàm raka, andǝ tsǝkɓalǝu mǝgule ka,
\v 17 ɓǝ̀ ɓak ɓabum wun sǝ ɓǝ̀ pà wun rǝcandǝa mala pě andǝ ne mǝɓoarne.
\c 3
\s1 Bulǝs zǝmba ama ɓǝa tsǝì aɓa hiwi
\p 
\v 1 A masǝlǝate ka, wun amǝ'eamrǝarǝu, wu tsǝk sǝm aɓa hiwi, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ Cau mala Mǝtalabangŋo ɓǝ̀ lidǝmba, ɓǝ̀ akiban a ban aɓwana kat nǝ mire, sǝ ɓǝa é nǝ gusǝlǝban kǝla mǝnana pa aɓalǝ wun ngga.
\v 2 Wu kǝ pak hiwi ɗǝm ama, Ɓakuli nǝ̀ bwala sǝm nggam, nǝ̀ amsǝ sǝm a bu aɓwana amǝɓane, amǝ'ɓealɓikea. Acemǝnana aɓwana kat sǝ à paɓamuria a ban Mǝtalabangŋo Yesu ɗàng.
\v 3 Sǝ Mǝtalabangŋo ka, à nǝ̀ gūlì arǝì. Nǝ̀ pa wun rǝcandǝa, nǝ̀ yál wun a bu yì Mǝɓealɓikea.
\v 4 Sǝm ndanǝ makɓalǝu arǝ Mǝtalabangŋo amur wun ama, wu nda aban pak agir mǝnana sǝm bangga wun ngga, sǝ wu nǝ̀ lidǝmba nǝ pea.
\v 5 Ən nggǝ zǝmba ɓǝ̀ Mǝtalabangŋo kyan nǝ ɓabum wun arǝ lǝmdǝ earcearǝu ulang mala Ɓakuli, andǝ do gandǝrǝu mana Kǝrǝsti kǝ pâ ka.
\s1 Nunkiru arǝ do ɓà
\p 
\v 6 Wun amǝ'eamrǝarǝu, sǝm nggǝ na wun aɓa lullǝ Mǝtala sǝm Yesu Kǝrǝsti ama, wu purî njar mala aɓwana mǝnana à na ama yia ka amǝkpata Yesu na, sǝ à kǝ dukdo nkundǝr, à kǝ kpata agir mǝnana sǝm kania wun ngga raka.
\v 7 Wun nǝ ɓamur rǝ wun ngga, wu sǝlǝna ama ɓoaro ɓǝ̀ wu twal kusǝ sǝm. Sǝm ngga, sǝm duk do nkundǝr aɓalǝ wun ɗàng.
\v 8 Sǝm li girlina mala kǝɓwa sǝ sǝm ginǝ mbwe gìr a kúnì ɗàng. Sǝm pak túró nǝ rǝcandǝa ma'sǝm du andǝ pwari, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm ngga duk twalo amur kǝɓwa ɗàng.
\v 9 Sǝm ngga, sǝm ndanǝ rǝcandǝa mǝnana sǝm nǝ̀ na wun ama ɓǝ̀ wu pa sǝm girlina ka, sǝ sǝm pe anggo ɗàng acemǝnana sǝm earce dupa wun gìrkànì.
\v 10 Sǝ mǝnana sǝm nda aɓalǝ wun ɗiɗyal ka, sǝm nggǝ na wun ama, <<Ɓwa mǝnana kat ɓinǝe, pà nǝ̀ pak túró raka, ɓǝ̀ kǝa li girlina gbal ɗàng.>>
\p 
\v 11 Sǝm bang anggo, acemǝnana sǝm nggǝ ok ama, aɓea aɓwana nda aɓalǝ wun mǝnana à kǝ dukdo ɓana, à kǝ pak kǝ túró raka. Kǝ túró malea nda kutiki aɓalǝ acau mala aɓwana.
\v 12 Aɓa lullǝ Mǝtalabangŋo Yesu Kǝrǝsti ka, sǝm nggǝ cia sǝ sǝm nggǝ zǝmbia wia, ɓǝa dum nǝ hamírǝu, ɓǝa pǝlǝ buia, ace mǝnana ɓǝa linǝ ɓamuria ka.
\v 13 Sǝ wun, amǝ'eambǝam ngga, wu kǝa aulǝ nǝ pěmǝɓoarne ɗàng.
\p 
\v 14 Wu tsǝkir wun arǝ ɓwa mǝnana ɓinǝ kpata cau mǝnana sǝm ne aɓa mǝnia yì cauterǝa ka. Wu purî njargula male, ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ kǝsǝkya kumi.
\v 15 Sǝ wu kǝa twali kǝla ɓi wun mǝbura ɗang, wu nunkiri, kǝla mǝ'eam wun.
\s1 Masǝlǝata makkun mala Bulǝs
\p 
\v 16 Ado ka, ɓǝ̀ Mǝtala dorǝpwala nǝ nggearǝì, pa wun dorǝpwala ko aya pwari, a koya njargula kat. Mǝtalabangŋo ɓǝ̀ do atà wun kat.
\p 
\v 17 Mim Bulǝs ka, nǝ buam sǝ ǝn gilǝ mǝnia yì makkun ngga. Mim ngga, anggo sǝ ǝn nggǝ tsǝk buam arǝ koya cauterǝa mem; anggo sǝ ǝn nggǝ gilǝgir.
\v 18 Ɓǝ̀ ɓwamuru mala Mǝtala sǝm Yesu Kǝrǝsti, do atà wun kat.
